data.description: Welcome to this stunning 2-story home, graced with stone accents on its facade, a cozy front porch, and an RV gate. Spacious main bedroom is a serene sanctuary offering an ensuite with dual sinks, a soothing tub, and a walk-in closet. Cozy loft can be used as a home office or a creative space. Unwind in the backyard, which features a covered patio, a charming Ramada, sheds, and a refreshing heated pool, perfect for entertaining. Water softener, R/O system, 2 fridges, wine fridge, kitchen TV, washer and dryer, blink cameras all STAY! This home has PAID OFF Solar as well! This gem won't disappoint! Don't miss it!
